title: Resume Magic - Susan Britton Whitcomb
description: All the tricks professional resume writers use to create eye-catching, results-driven resumes are revealed in this must-have guide. Renowned as the definitive resource for writing and designing resumes, Resume Magic combines great tips with before-and-after resume transformations to explain the 'nuts and bolts' of resume creation. Author Susan Britton Whitcomb connects professional techniques with actual examples to demonstrate why the techniques work. Any college student, recent graduate, or job-seeking adult will use the strategies and advice provided in this book a thousand times over
